## Updated Tech Decisions (Changes from Design Doc)

| Area | Design Doc | Implementation | Reason |
|------|-----------|----------------|--------|
| Embedding Model | `text-embedding-004` (768-dim) | `gemini-embedding-001` (3072-dim) | text-embedding-004 deprecated Jan 2026 |
| Vector DB (Phase 1) | Qdrant Cloud | Supabase pgvector | Fewer services to manage initially |
